# Cloudflare Workers static-assets redirects (wrangler.jsonc assets dir = ./;
# host of record since 2026-07-17). nginx (the Railway fallback) carries the
# same redirect in nginx.conf WITH the #home-repair fragment; fragment support
# is undocumented for CF-style _redirects files, so it is intentionally
# omitted here. Both the .html and the extensionless form are listed because
# CF's html_handling serves lane pages at extensionless URLs (.html 307s).
/home-repair.html /residential-construction.html 301
/home-repair /residential-construction 301
